    <scopecontent>
      <head>Collection Overview</head>
      <p>The materials in the Beatrice Witkin Papers range from her earliest musical compositions to her major works.  Notes and secondary literature accompany many of the compositions, and all major works have complete scores. 
</p>
      <arrangement>
        <head>Collection Arrangement</head>
        <p>The works follow a chronological order in each box.</p>
      </arrangement>
    </scopecontent>
